headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium: Överflöd Entity XF
content: Whether you’re waking up in the Penthouse or on the bathroom floor, swing by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort at any time to spin the Lucky Wheel. You’ll walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, plus all kinds of mystery prizes. The top reward on the podium is a potent symbol of invention, innovation, and reckless efficiency: the Överflöd Entity XF.
